{"tid":414509,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★外國大量網民投訴更新 iOS 11 後經常 App 崩潰和死機","createTime":"2017-09-26T09:41:35.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-26T11:53:35.000Z","uid":19454,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"783de80145959daa62abb331c92a84426a014bc3","tid":414509,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"每次改版升級 iOS，App 的速度會一如預期變慢，但是對網民來說，今次升級 iOS 11 後 App 的反應似乎令網民不太滿意。<br />\n<br />\n在 Reddit 討論區，有為數不少的網民投訴升級 iOS 11 升級之後應用程式速度變慢、崩潰退出以及發現不同的問題，其中網民 leejoness 形容升級 iOS 11 後開 App 相當粗重，不論是 Safari、Reddit、ESPN、Yahoo&hellip;&hellip;都遇上崩潰、變慢甚至停留不動，而這些問題在未升級之前沒有出現，但升級之後 2 日，他需要重設手機 2 次。<br />\n[img]<a href=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/netizen-complain-ios-11-crash_01.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fnetizen-complain-ios-11-crash_01.png&d=Fp5P8YFNQeoso2gePw%2BPvKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=06b5dde2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/netizen-complain-ios-11-crash_01.png</a><br />\n[/img]<br />\n<br />\n當你以為 leejoness 的問題是個別事件？但不少網民有同感，網民 freshairr 就指他升級 iOS 11 beta 沒有這種問題，但自從升級 GM 之後問題就出現了，App 不能啟動或崩潰退出，所有 iOS 運作變慢，甚至連藍牙控制也有問題。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.newmobilelife.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/09/netizen-complain-ios-11-crash_02.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.newmobilelife.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F09%2Fnetizen-complain-ios-11-crash_02.png&h=b6d26ae9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/09/26/netizen-complain-ios-11-crash/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newmobilelife.com%2F2017%2F09%2F26%2Fnetizen-complain-ios-11-crash%2F&d=Fp5P8YFNQeoso2gePw%2BPvKS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=1e001491\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.newmobilelife.com/2017/09/26/netizen-complain-ios-11-crash/</a>"},{"pid